  "body": "Hi there,\r\n\r\nI have modified ```calcDifficulty()``` , ```calcDifficultyByzantium()``` , ```calcDifficultyHomestead()``` and ```calcDifficultyFrontier()``` to return big1 . now difficulty grows far slower but still grows (after mining about 1400 ether difficulty is about 260). how to complitely fix it?\r\n\r\nI have a separate problem, too:\r\nI have set gasPrice to zero using miner.setGasPrice(0) in geth console but still command eth.gasPrice returns diffault 18000000000 value so I have no way to send ether in my ethereum wallet gui with total cost of sent ether.\r\n\r\nwhat's different between miner.setGasPrice(0) and eth.gasPrice and what should I do?",
